  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roboban: Colors is a single-player Sokoban-style puzzle video game in which you control robots that must reach their charging stations, but not before placing the boxes in their respective destinations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877570/extras/e933b370ead83e401eae85fbce5d7966.poster.avif?t=1738854455\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877570/extras/e933b370ead83e401eae85fbce5d7966.webm?t=1738854455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877570/extras/e933b370ead83e401eae85fbce5d7966.mp4?t=1738854455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have the help of several robots to complete the challenges that will be presented to you in each level, and you will be able to choose the color of the robots you want to control at any time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877570/extras/1391211aad7f5e4a2a3dbe6797609938.poster.avif?t=1738854455\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877570/extras/1391211aad7f5e4a2a3dbe6797609938.webm?t=1738854455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877570/extras/1391211aad7f5e4a2a3dbe6797609938.mp4?t=1738854455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The levels are divided into 4 worlds where you will find new obstacles that will make each level more challenging. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 90 handmade levels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Undo function. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute robots. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to test your wits?</p>",
